#Dummy CleanTextTools

A lightweight Python utility package that provides simple and efficient string-cleaning functions.  
Designed for developers who need quick preprocessing of text, code, or HTML snippets.

---

## âœ¨ Features

This package includes **four core functions**:

- Remove a specific character from a string
- Remove HTML angle brackets and slashes (`<`, `>`, `/`)
- Remove all spaces from code or text
- Display a built-in help menu describing all available functions

